my The Free\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a different experience.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different experience\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I obviously spend more time warming up, more time in recovery and just make sure I look after my body,\\\" said Gunn.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"recovery\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think a 20-year-old needs to worry as much about those things.\\\"\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 20-year-old needs\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two gold medals are up for grabs in the breaking competition in Paris, one each for the best male and female dancer, .\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999964012314376, \"rank\": 3.5987813315696312e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two gold medals\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2228}, {\"ngram\": \"grabs\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"the breaking competition\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"the best male and female dancer\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dancers, who call themselves \\\"B-boys\\\" and \\\"B-girls\\\", compete in one-on-one battles in three, minute-long \\\"throw downs\\\", with the music chosen by a DJ and performances scored by a panel of judges.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dancers\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"B-boys\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"B-girls\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"one-on-one battles\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"downs\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2450}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"a DJ\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"performances\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"a panel\", \"from\": 2510, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking was popular at the Youth Olympics in Buenos Aires in 2018 and drew enthusiastic crowds at its Asian Games debut in China last year.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 0.9999999801043489, \"rank\": 1.9522199098059663e-08, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}, {\"begin\": 2654, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9875440029673338, \"rank\": 0.006898627919050799, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"the Youth Olympics\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiastic crowds\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"its Asian Games debut\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, its addition to the Olympic programme has had its detractors, who have dismissed it as a desperate ploy by the International Olympic Committee to attract a younger audience.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its addition\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2693}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic programme\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2718}, {\"ngram\": \"its detractors\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"a desperate ploy\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2784}, {\"ngram\": \"a younger audience\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some dancers are also sceptical about how breaking's underground roots and street culture fit the commercialised Olympic movement.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some dancers\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"how breaking's underground roots\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"street culture\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"the commercialised Olympic movement\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The critics may be happy that Los Angeles Olympic organisers declined to retain breaking for the 2028 Games.\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999997598934, \"rank\": 2.3094627572547027e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp