 \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Breaking has such a positive force and impact on people's lives that do it,\\\" said Gunn.\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3527, \"end\": 3531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3453}, {\"ngram\": \"such a positive force\", \"from\": 3458, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"impact\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3490}, {\"ngram\": \"people's lives\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They get fit, they get a creative outlet and become part of this community.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a creative outlet\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3575}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3591}, {\"ngram\": \"this community\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The platform that the Olympics gives us to inspire new generations of people is positive.\\\"\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The platform\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3623}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3641}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"new generations\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3677}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3746}]}]}"